(1021, '_transient_mashshare_add_ons_feed', '               \r\n \r\n						<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Add more social networks</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-social-networks-addon/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mash-networks-e1404756641988.png\" alt=\"Mashshare More Networks\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>Extend Mashshare: Google+, Whatsapp, Pinterest, Digg, Linkedin, Reddit, Stumbleupon, Vk,Print, Delicious, Buffer, Weibo, Pocket, Xing, Tumblr …<a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-social-networks-addon/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">VideoPost Popup</h3>\n<p><a title=\"VideoPost Popup Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/videopost-popup/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/03/videopost1.png\" alt=\"VideoPost Popup\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>Share and Like Add-On for Facebook and Twitter which shows an Popup after end of YouTube Video play or read of a story. <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/videopost-popup/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Performance Widget</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Mashshare Performance Widget Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/performance-widget?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/07/performance.png\" alt=\"Mashshare Performance Widget Add-On\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nShares, comments and real time reads at a glance. Give your website a great visual social impact. <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Performance Widget Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/performance-widget?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Sticky ShareBar</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/sticky-sharebar/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/10/sharebar.png\" alt=\"Sticky ShareBar\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nFull responsive all time visible ShareBar on top or bottom of your page which slides down after scrolling.<a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Sticky ShareBar\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/sticky-sharebar/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Realtime Pageview Counter</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-pageviews/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-6713 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/10/pageviews-300x187.png\" alt=\"Pageviews Realtime Counter\" width=\"300\" height=\"187\" /><br />\n</a>Realtime Pageview Counter &#8211; Increase user interaction and interest with this ajax based Pageview Counter<a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Pageview Counter\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-pageviews/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Sticky Facebook LikeBar</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Mashshare Networks Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/facebook-like-bar?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/01/fblike.png\" alt=\"Mashshare Sticky facebook like bar\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nA highly customizable, full responsive and mobile optimized sticky Like-Bar <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Like-Bar\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/facebook-like-bar?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Google Analytics Integration</h3>\n<p><a title=\"Google Analytics Integration\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/google-analytics-integration/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4273 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/09/google-analytics.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /><br />\n</a>Track and count clicks on all Share Buttons within your Google Analytics account in realtime  <a title=\"Google Analytics Integration\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/google-analytics-integration/\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Add responsive style</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-responsive/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-494 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/mashshare-responsive.png\" alt=\"mashshare-responsive\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nAdd responsive style to Mashshare <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare responsive Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-responsive/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">ShortURLs Integration</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/shorturls-integration/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-5207 size-medium\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/10/shorturls-300x187.png\" alt=\"shorturls\" width=\"300\" height=\"187\" /></a><br />\nAdd shortURLs for Twitter <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Shorturls Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/shorturls-integration/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Like Pop-Up after Share</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-likeaftershare/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-107 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/08/likeaftershare1.jpg\" alt=\"mash-networks\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nShare a post and get a Facebook Like Pop-Up overlay as seen on <a href=\"http://heftig.co\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow\" rel=\"nofollow\" >heftig.co</a> or <a href=\"http://www.sfglobe.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow\" rel=\"nofollow\" >sfglobe.com</a>. <a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare LikeAfterShare Add-On\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-likeaftershare/?ref=1\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Mashshare Open Graph</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-open-graph/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4472 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2014/09/open-graph.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nShare your content in the best possible way<br />\nSocial sharing optimization with Open Graph implementation<br />\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Mashshare Open Graph\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/mashshare-open-graph/\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mashshare-addons\">\n<h3 class=\"mashshare-addons-title\">Social Locker &#8211; 3rd Party</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/social-locker-plugin-pay-with-a-like/\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-4472 size-full\" src=\"https://www.mashshare.net/wp-content/uploads/edd/2015/03/sociallocker-mashshare.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a><br />\nSocial Locker locks your site content behind a set of social buttons until the visitor likes, shares, +1s.<br />\n<a class=\"button-secondary\" title=\"Social Locker\" href=\"https://www.mashshare.net/downloads/social-locker-plugin-pay-with-a-like/\" target=\"_blank\">Get this Add On</a></p>\n</div>\n\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n               \r\n \r\n						\r\n    \r\n        ', 'no'),
